entries.title: Mother of rape survivor Katie Shone, 38, pays touching tribute to 'loved' daughter
entries.description: Katie Shone's mother, Susan Stothard, wants her beloved daughter to be remembered for her glowing smile, her humour, and her efforts to go 'above and beyond to be a good friend and daughter'.

entries.title: London council rebels against Sadiq Khan's ULEZ expansion by refusing traffic camera installation
entries.description: Sutton has vowed to fight the expansion of Sadiq Khan's Ultra Low Emission Zone (ULEZ) forcing around 200,000 more vehicles a day to pay £12.50 to drive in the capital.

entries.title: Hormone replacement therapy may lower chance of developing Alzheimer's in women with high-risk gene
entries.description: Taking the menopause drug was linked with better memory, cognitive function and larger brain volumes in later life in women carrying a gene called APOE4.

entries.title: Dominic Perrottet offered to remove Nazi uniform at party
entries.description: During a special press conference on Thursday, Mr Perrottet, 40, said he was 'naive' and regretted the decision to wear the costume in September, 2003.

entries.title: Omar Zakaria, father of Australia's most wanted man Masood Zakaria faces court at Parramatta, Sydney
entries.description: The father of a gang leader who fled Australia has faced court after allegedly hiding hundreds of thousands of his son's crime money at his western Sydney home.

entries.title: Family kept the mummified remains of their daughter because they were convinced she was still alive
entries.description: Rina Yasutake, 49, of Helmsley, North Yorkshire wasted away from a lack of food before found by police. Northallerton Coroner's Court found no suggestion of suspicious circumstances.

entries.title: NHS boss says hospitals are 'over-reliant' on foreign staff
entries.description: The head of the NHS has demanded more places for home-grown doctors and nurses at medical schools and warns hospitals are 'over-reliant' on foreign staff.

entries.title: TOM LEONARD explains why top-secret files found on Joe Biden's garage could wreck his Presidency
entries.description: Joe Biden didn't hold back when asked for his thoughts after seeing a photo of top secret documents from his predecessor stashed away at Donald Trump's Mar-a-Lago home in Florida.

entries.title: Hard-left doctors used 'Marxist' tactics to secure the leadership of the British Medical Association
entries.description: Hard-Left doctors who used Marxist tactics to secure the leadership of the British Medical Association are pushing for co-ordinated strikes with other unions.
